      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANOTHER SCRUB (6) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 0.8 lengths back in second (24.11) at this track in a Grade 6 over 407m. Capable of going well again. HEROIC HENRY (2) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when third (25.99) in a Grade 6 over 457m at Q Lakeside. Rates a winning chance on best. POOKIE BEAR (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (19.97) at Q Lakeside behind Golden Legs in a Grade 6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature again. PACKHAM ROSE (4) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
